== 製作 ==
2016年3月，在《[[自殺突擊隊|自殺突擊隊]]》中與導演[[大衛·艾亞|大衛·艾亞]]合作的[[威爾·史密斯|威爾·史密斯]]將再度合作參與《光靈》。該片被描述為「一部現代警察驚悚片，但含有奇幻的元素」，由史密斯與[[喬爾·埃哲頓|喬爾·埃哲頓]]主演，[[麥克斯·蘭迪斯|麥克斯·蘭迪斯]]負責編劇<ref>{{cite news|url=http://collider.com/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-joel-edgerton/|title=David Ayer to Direct Will Smith and Joel Edgerton in Fantastical Cop Flick ‘Bright’|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2017-05-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170512201922/http://collider.com/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-joel-edgerton/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-suicide-squad-1201696226/|title=Will Smith, David Ayer Reteaming on Max Landis Spec ‘Bright’|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2016-06-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160625091402/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/will-smith-david-ayer-bright-suicide-squad-1201696226/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在[[Netflix|Netflix]]取得發行權後，電影預計從2016年秋季起開始拍攝，其預算將高達9000萬美元<ref>{{cite news|url=http://collider.com/netflix-bright-deal-will-smith-david-ayer-movie/|title=Netflix Makes Mammoth Deal for David Ayer’s ‘Bright’ Starring Will Smith|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320113911/http://collider.com/netflix-bright-deal-will-smith-david-ayer-movie/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。演員[[歐蜜·瑞佩斯|歐蜜·瑞佩斯]]於2016年5月加入參與演出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://screenrant.com/noomi-rapace-will-smith-bright-david-ayer/|title=Noomi Rapace in Talks to Join Will Smith in David Ayer’s Bright|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2019-02-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190205063700/https://screenrant.com/noomi-rapace-will-smith-bright-david-ayer/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。蘭迪斯受訪時表示，製作將於2016年9月開始，但他們已經在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]拍攝了一小部分<ref>{{cite news|url=http://collider.com/max-landis-bright-star-wars-interview/|title=Watch: Max Landis Hopes ‘Bright’ Will Be His ‘Star Wars’|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2020-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201010214103/http://collider.com/max-landis-bright-star-wars-interview/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與艾亞時常合作的攝影師[[羅曼·瓦夏諾夫|羅曼·瓦夏諾夫]]被再次聘請來掌鏡<ref>{{cite news|url=http://nofilmschool.com/2016/08/cinematographer-roman-vasyanov-shoots-anamorphic-suicide-squad|title=Why DP Roman Vasyanov Chose Anamorphic & More Tales from Shooting 'Suicide Squad'|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108172403/http://nofilmschool.com/2016/08/cinematographer-roman-vasyanov-shoots-anamorphic-suicide-squad|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年10月15日，{{le|露西·佛瑞|Lucy Fry}}加入演出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/david-ayers-bright-lands-lucy-937362|title=David Ayer's 'Bright' Lands 'Mr. Church' Actress Lucy Fry (Exclusive)|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2016-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121194556/http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/david-ayers-bright-lands-lucy-937362|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年10月17日，{{le|安德莉亞·娜菲道|Andrea Navedo}}也參演了電影<ref>{{cite news|url=http://deadline.com/2016/10/davie-ayer-netflix-bright-andrea-navedo-austin-hebert-burden-movie-1201837579/|title=David Ayer-Helmed Thriller ‘Bright’ Adds Andrea Navedo; Austin Hébert Cast In ‘Burden’|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108112901/https://deadline.com/2016/10/davie-ayer-netflix-bright-andrea-navedo-austin-hebert-burden-movie-1201837579/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年10月20日，宣布{{le|布萊德·威廉·亨克|Brad William Henke}}簽約加入演出<ref>{{cite news|url=http://variety.com/2016/tv/news/brad-william-henke-cast-bright-netflix-1201893119/|title=‘Orange Is the New Black’ Actor Brad William Henke Joins Will Smith in ‘Bright’ (EXCLUSIVE)|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108111608/https://variety.com/2016/tv/news/brad-william-henke-cast-bright-netflix-1201893119/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年11月1日，{{le|肯尼斯·崔|Kenneth Choi}}和{{le|黛恩·歐利維莉|Dawn Olivieri}}將分別飾演未知角色及史密斯角色的妻子<ref>{{cite news|url=http://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/david-ayers-fantasy-cop-thriller-bright-adds-two/|title=David Ayer’s Fantasy Cop Thriller Bright Adds Two|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-09-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180924224945/https://wegotthiscovered.com/movies/david-ayers-fantasy-cop-thriller-bright-adds-two/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。11月9日，[[艾格·拉米瑞茲|艾格·拉米瑞茲]]已被證實簽約參演<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/edgar-ramirez-joins-will-smith-david-ayers-fantasy-thriller-bright-946000|title=Edgar Ramirez Joins Will Smith in David Ayer's Fantasy Thriller 'Bright' (Exclusive)|accessdate=2017-03-02|archive-date=2018-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180925025417/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/heat-vision/edgar-ramirez-joins-will-smith-david-ayers-fantasy-thriller-bright-946000|dead-url=no}}</ref>。同月，[[艾歷斯·梅拉|艾歷斯·梅拉]]、{{le|麥特·傑拉德|Matt Gerald}}、[[艾克·拜瑞豪茲|艾克·拜瑞豪茲]]與[[恩里克·莫西亞諾|恩里克·莫西亞諾]]都已加入參與該片的演出<ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/ashley-bell-next-door-alex-meraz-bright-david-ayer-1201853108/|title=Ashley Bell Cast As Lead In ‘Next Door’; Alex Meraz Joins David Ayer’s ‘Bright’|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2016-11-11|accessdate=2016-11-16|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108141014/https://deadline.com/2016/11/ashley-bell-next-door-alex-meraz-bright-david-ayer-1201853108/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/matt-herald-bright-netflix-angel-bonanni-entebbe-movie-1201854961/|title=Matt Gerald Boards David Ayer’s ‘Bright’; Angel Bonanni Cast In ‘Entebbe’|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2016-11-15|accessdate=2016-11-16|archive-date=2019-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191011010514/https://deadline.com/2016/11/matt-herald-bright-netflix-angel-bonanni-entebbe-movie-1201854961/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/ike-barinholtz-bright-reunites-david-ayer-will-smith-netflix-1201855549/|title=Ike Barinholtz Reunites With David Ayer, Will Smith On Netflix Film ‘Bright|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Mike|last=Fleming Jr|date=2016-11-16|accessdate=2016-11-16|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023212517/https://deadline.com/2016/11/ike-barinholtz-bright-reunites-david-ayer-will-smith-netflix-1201855549/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/11/enrique-murciano-netflix-bright-movie-1201858381/|title=Enrique Murciano Cast In Netflix’s ‘Bright|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Amanda|last=N'Duka|date=2016-11-22|accessdate=2016-11-22|archive-date=2020-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107022431/https://deadline.com/2016/11/enrique-murciano-netflix-bright-movie-1201858381/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

